Examples

library("DALEXtra")
library("mlr")
task <- mlr::makeRegrTask(
  id = "R",
  data = apartments,
  target = "m2.price"
)
learner_lm <- mlr::makeLearner(
  "regr.lm"
)
model_lm <- mlr::train(learner_lm, task)
explainer_lm <- explain_mlr(model_lm, apartmentsTest, apartmentsTest$m2.price, label = "LM")
